OL,5,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FA look at how high-speed pursuits
OL,7,     Fof 'drivers failing to stop' cause
OL,8,     Faround 40 deaths a year on
OL,9,     FBritain's roads. Jamie Theakston
OL,10,     Fpresents.
OL,11,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,12,     FDealing with drug users and
OL,13,     Fdealers is a daily challenge for
OL,14,     Fcops. A driver, suspected of being
OL,15,     Funder the influence of drugs,
OL,16,     Ftries to evade capture, including
OL,17,     Framming a police car.
OL,18,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,19,     FDamo and the firearms team tackle
OL,20,     Fa supermarket gunman, while Gareth
OL,21,     Ffaces a death-defying pursuit
OL,22,     Falong roads and back alleys.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
