OL,5,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FBen Sutcliffe takes presenter Rick
OL,7,     FEdwards through interceptor
OL,8,     Ftraining. And Kev Salter goes on
OL,9,     Fdrugs busts, accompanied by rookie
OL,10,     FPete Tate on two of them.
OL,11,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,12,     FA collection of some of the most
OL,13,     Fextreme chases the Interceptors
OL,14,     Fhave been involved in, including a
OL,15,     Fhot pursuit through a housing
OL,16,     Festate.
