OL,5,G1700 Call the Bailiffs: Time to Pay Up
OL,6,     FAgents Chris and Gavyn visit a man
OL,7,     Fwhose company owes a client a
OL,8,     Frefund for money paid upfront for
OL,9,     Fa car restoration. The owner is
OL,10,     Fwell-meaning, but says he is
OL,11,     Funable to pay.
OL,12,G1800 Home and Away
OL,13,     FSonny pushes beyond his limits.
OL,14,     FLeah fights for Alf's reputation.
OL,15,     FDavid struggles with small-town
OL,16,     Fpolicing.
OL,17,G1830 New: Home and Away
OL,18,     FSonny refuses to play by the
OL,19,     Frules. Cash's turnaround is
OL,20,     Fshort-lived. Justin catches a
OL,21,     Flucky break.
