OL,5,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FThis week the staff at the Hall
OL,7,     FGreen Health Centre in Birmingham
OL,8,     Fare getting ready for another busy
OL,9,     Fweek.
OL,10,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,11,     FDocumentary series filmed inside
OL,12,     FBarnsley casualty department. A
OL,13,     Fbusy Monday becomes a
OL,14,     Frecord-breaker as the team deal
OL,15,     Fwith 349 patients.
OL,16,G2100 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,17,     FAn air ambulance is sent to help a
OL,18,     Ftree surgeon impaled on metal
OL,19,     Frailings; a 6-year-old is rushed
OL,20,     Fto hospital for head injuries; a
OL,21,     Fdouble amputee is found lying in a
OL,22,     Fpool of blood.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
